### Create a Product
POST https://localhost:7000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance gaming laptop with RTX 4080",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "stockQuantity": 50
}

### Get All Products
GET https://localhost:7000/api/products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### Get Products with Filter
GET https://localhost:7000/api/products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&nameFilter=laptop

### Get Product by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/products/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

### Update Product (replace with actual ID and RowVersion)
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/products/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop Pro",
  "description": "Updated high-performance gaming laptop with RTX 4090",
  "price": 1599.99,
  "stockQuantity": 45,
  "rowVersion": "AAAAAAAAB9E="
}

### Delete Product (replace with actual ID)
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/products/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

### Place an Order (replace with actual product ID)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### Place Multiple Item Order
POST https://localhost:7000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "productId": "87654321-4321-4321-4321-210987654321",
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}